name: Chem Cake
description: Chem Cake is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Birthday Cake and Chem D. This strain is 60% sativa and 40% indica. Chem Cake is 28% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Bred by Hytiva, the average price of Chem Cake typically ranges from $10-$15 per gram.
